data.description: Welcome to your next home. This 3 bedroom 2.5 bath has a great curb appeal and a wonderful layout with an open living area, tall ceilings, gas fireplace, formal dining room and an eat in kitchen. Master bedroom on main level and two bedrooms and a bath on the second level with a balcony hallway. Refrigerator, water and dryer convey along with Samsung ATMOS sound system with the soundbar built into the mantel. This home is priced to sell, call for your showing today
